WEBVTT Offset: 0.864;

00:00:09.476 --> 00:00:13.512
<lang ja>思いを馳せるのって
干渉もできない
<lang en>"Thinking back in time." It's frustrating.

00:00:13.512 --> 00:00:17.889
<lang ja>タイムマシンみたいで
なんか歯痒いね
<lang en>It's like a time machine that
can't interfere with anything.

00:00:17.889 --> 00:00:21.469
<lang ja>3Dのレンズして感動だけ貰って
<lang en>I just want to put on my 3D glasses and be impressed.

00:00:21.469 --> 00:00:25.731
<lang ja>ポップコーンつまんで
覗いていたいね
<lang en>I just want to peek through them
while eating popcorn.

00:00:25.731 --> 00:00:30.116
<lang ja>何か落とした気がして戻った
教室の灯り消えて暗いはずなのに
<lang en>I came back because I thought I dropped something.
The lights were off in the classroom

00:00:30.116 --> 00:00:34.106
<lang ja>誰かいるような気がして
ドア開けたら十数年前の俺じゃん！
<lang en>But I felt like there was someone in there,
I open the door and it's me from a decade ago!

00:00:34.106 --> 00:00:38.103
<lang ja>大人になってなんでもなれると
思い込んでたらやっぱ苦労したね
<lang en>I thought I could be anything I wanted to be when I grew up, 
but I knew I'd have a hard time.

00:00:38.103 --> 00:00:41.117
<lang ja>までもおかげで知り合えた人たちもいるし
いい歌詞かけるし
<lang en>But I've gotten to know some people,
and I can put on some good lyrics.

00:00:41.117 --> 00:00:42.116
<lang ja>トントンってことで！
<lang en>I'll take it easy!

00:00:42.116 --> 00:00:52.108
<lang ja>あぁいつか
この景色も切り取られてアルバムになるから…
<lang en>Someday this view will be cut out
and made into an album.

00:00:52.108 --> 00:00:58.905
<lang ja>そしたら君に
話してあげるよ多分
<lang en>I'll tell you about that then.
Maybe.

00:00:58.905 --> 00:01:03.116
<lang ja>そろそろ帰んなきゃね
習い事の時間だったね
<lang en>I should probably get going.
It's time for my lesson.

00:01:03.116 --> 00:01:07.210
<lang ja>木の葉の浮かぶプールサイド
校舎の裏の車道
<lang en>By the pool with the leaves floating in the trees,
and the driveway behind the school building.

00:01:07.210 --> 00:01:11.342
<lang ja>ハッキリしなきゃだなんて…
いややっぱりやめとこうって
<lang en>Do I need to clarify?
I knew I shouldn't have.

00:01:11.342 --> 00:01:15.699
<lang ja>持ち帰る鞄と手紙と…どんなに素敵だろう！
<lang en>I'll take the bag and the letter home.
How wonderful!

00:01:15.699 --> 00:01:19.296
<lang ja>どんどん加速してる
鼓動音を追い越してる
<lang en>It's accelerating.
It's overtaking the sound of your heartbeat.

00:01:19.296 --> 00:01:24.079
<lang ja>もう見えなくなるくらいに
弧を描いてる光
<lang en>I can't see it anymore.
The light that's arcing.

00:01:24.079 --> 00:01:27.699
<lang ja>どんどん加速してる
鼓動音を追い越してる
<lang en>It's accelerating faster and faster.
It's overtaking the sound of my heartbeat.

00:01:27.699 --> 00:01:31.873
<lang ja>もう見えなくなるくらいに
ノスタルジックマジック！
<lang en>So fast that you can't see it anymore,
It's Nostalgic magic!

00:01:31.873 --> 00:01:36.123
<lang ja>息継ぎもせず一気に
4、5メーターほど泳いだら
<lang en>All at once without even a breath.
I swam about four or five meters.

00:01:36.123 --> 00:01:40.334
<lang ja>花火のようなこの数年間も
少しくらい報われるかな
<lang en>I'd be a little rewarded for
all these years of fireworks.

00:01:40.334 --> 00:01:44.436
<lang ja>ひたすら企みもなく、がむしゃらに
自分の形を確かめるように
<lang en>I've spent them all without a plan,
just going through the motions, as if to check my own shape.

00:01:44.436 --> 00:01:46.436
<lang ja>もうお開き、青春おしまい！
<lang en>I'm done, my youth is over!

00:01:46.436 --> 00:01:48.500
<lang ja>第2章も…乞うご期待！ 
<lang en>Chapter 2...stay tuned!

00:01:48.500 --> 00:01:58.139
<lang ja>ねぇ、いつか…
あの景色と違うアルバムのページになるから
<lang en>Hey, someday...
you'll have a different view and a different page in your album.

00:01:58.139 --> 00:02:05.015
<lang ja>そしたら、きっと許してあげるよ多分
<lang en>And then maybe I'll forgive you.

00:02:05.015 --> 00:02:09.309
<lang ja>そろそろ帰んなきゃね
アルバイトの時間だったね
<lang en>I should probably get going.
It's time for my part-time job.

00:02:09.309 --> 00:02:13.365
<lang ja>塗り重ねた階段の手すりと踊っていたいかも 
<lang en>I might want to dance with
the painted railing on the stairs.

00:02:13.365 --> 00:02:17.473
<lang ja>さよなら…やっと言えたね
放課後、自転車置き場で
<lang en>Goodbye... finally.
After school, at the bike yard.

00:02:17.473 --> 00:02:19.752
<lang ja>振り返るスローモーション、カットバック
<lang en>Looking back, slow motion, cut back

00:02:19.752 --> 00:02:22.141
<lang ja>どんなに素敵だろう！
<lang en>How wonderful!

